+**Import surface:** User-shared builds — i.e., a manually-authored or community-shared build
+configuration. This is **not** a "my actual character" import path; builds are imported from
+shared planner URLs that the user pastes into the tool. The import produces a Character with
+equipped items, skills, and paragon allocation matching the Maxroll planner, along with a
